5 monetary value, whether or not negotiable. Payment instrument does
6 not include stored value or any instrument to which either of the
7 following applies:
8 (i) It is redeemable by the issuer only for goods or services
9 provided by the issuer or its affiliate or franchisees of the
10 issuer or its affiliate, except to the extent required by
