23 Sec. 53. A person shall not engage in the business of money
24 transmission on behalf of a person not licensed under this act or
25 not exempt under article 3. A person that engages in such activity
26 provides money transmission to the same extent as if the person
27 were a licensee, and shall be jointly and severally liable with the
28 unlicensed or nonexempt person.
